<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #222222;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .order-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .order-table th,
        .order-table td {
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px;
        }

        .order-table th {
            background-color: #222222;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Order Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Thank you for your order, <%= user.name %>!</h2>
            <p>We are thrilled to have you as part of our learning community. Below are the details of your order:</p>

            <table class="order-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Order ID</th>
                        <th>Order Date</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>#<%= order._id %></td>
                        <td><%= order.date %></td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <h3>Courses Ordered:</h3>
            <table class="order-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Course Name</th>
                        <th>Price</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% order.items.forEach(item => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= item.name %></td>
                            <td>$<%= item.price.toFixed(2) %></td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 E-learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
